::Feline:;

"Oh well, one is enough I guess. I know, I don't like having to wear 
it either." She tossed the symbol away.  
"Well, shall we start?  Let's see, we'll need a believeable story or 
they may not allow us into the base.  Mine is that my pod landed and 
I was captured.  But I was able to escape from the naughty Allience 
and managed to find my way to the maximal base." She smiled and put 
her hands on her hips. "So what's your story going to be?" She looked 
him up and down and smiled. "Well handsome?"
